    "(3) Accent variations: Finally, we focus on 'text'-based research while acknowledging that the speech processing community has a rich history of using acoustic data centered around accent.",
    "To this end, we briefly touch upon speech since dialects and speech are intertwined to a certain degree.",
    "However, our primary focus is on text since the text aspect has received a lot more attention than the speech aspect.",
    "This also sets up a situation where a future survey can expand on the speech aspect of dialectal processing.",
    "The focus on the textual form is the typical purview of NLP."
